item.title: Black screening
item.dc:creator: @Timelimit10 Timelimit10
item.description:
@Timelimit10 wrote:

You probably altered something in your initialize boolean. check that. search client.java for initial or something like that. and youll find it. this is when the first packet is sent and recieved. this is also where the screen loads. which urs obviously isnt. if you have put in work elsewhere in your source i would download the original and just replace the whole initialize boolean.

its also possible its your account? try a different account
